name: The Goldtones EP
description:
The Goldtones highly anticipated self-titled debut EP. Encompassing infectious hook-lines and contagious choruses. A fresh infusion of pop-rock at its best.

50 pre-orders available with a limited edition and signed poster of The Goldtones- won't be available for long we're sure...

Release date: 3rd May 2010

Track Listings:
1. Night Time Lies
2. It's Alright
3. Next To Me
4. Turquoise

Grab a copy on Pre-Order now!

EP Launch Night and EP bundles are also available. 

(50p P+P U.K)
(£1.00 P+P Everywhere else)

Please note: Postage will be refunded if EP collected on Launch Night. Please state at time of purchase if you wish to receive the EP on the Launch Party date instead of being delivered.
